Starice::

Starice put the bottle in a table that was near her. She cleaned 
baby's mouth and continued speaking with sweet tone. "Well Little-
one" said sweetly Starice to Baby "You'll need a name... But wha 
twill be your name?"

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Moon Mist" <shadowwarrior_ax@h...> wrote:
> 
> Her paws twitched a little while she relaxed, tiny and smooth 
movements of 
> her limbs letting Starice know that she was starting to fall asleep.
> The baby was done eating and she moved her tiny mouth away from the 
end of 
> the bottle, still half the milk left in it but her tummy was tiny 
like her 
> body and full up already.
> She made a squeek, her own little kind of burp. Her tummy, for the 
first 
> time in a while, was round and full of warm milk.
> Her little eyes started to close and then open again, close and 
open again 
> until they closed for the last time and she fell into a very 
comfortable 
> snooze. Half asleep but half awake too.
>
